This file contains annotations for 500 sentences from English Wikipedia (column 1).  A word from the sentence was selected for simplification (column 2).  50 workers on Amazon's Mechanical Turk provided simplifications for the word in the context of the sentence (columns 3-52).

The file is a tab delimited file.

For more details and to cite, see:
Colby Horn, Katie Manduca and David Kauchak (2014). Learning a Lexical Simplifier Using Wikipedia. In Proceedings of ACL.

If you download this data and decide to use it, please send David Kauchak an e-mail.
